yt_dlp.title: Blackest Crow - Guitar 2 - AJAM Tune & Songbook
yt_dlp.description:
Song:  The Blackest Crow (As Time Draws Near)

Instrument: Guitar 2

Teacher: Carl Jones

Tuning: Standard

Recorded for Alleghany JAM (Junior Appalachian Musicians) after school music program.

This is a beautiful old song Tommy Jarrell sang with the banjo in D. 

Here it is arranged for fingerpick guitar in G (capo 7th fret to be in D). 

This is a review video for the Alleghany JAM Tune & Songbook which contains over a 100 pages of song words, chord photos, heritage musician bios plus fiddle, banjo, guitar, mandolin and dulcimer tablature, chords, and music. This book is available at www.alleghanyjam.com
